        "TileImage": "$($repository 42e7d00a-b477-4c4f-8b13-8cd4e7403e0d).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, agent. Before we take you off Sapienza, we need you to tie one last loose end for us. The new head of the local Mafia, who now answers to us thanks to you, has asked us to send a &quot;message&quot; to a local politician. He has been very vocal about fighting organized crime. We can&apos;t have that. Murder three members of his security details who are keeping watch over his rally. Do not fail us. Good hunting, agent.",
